org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.primitives

Class DynamicEnumParameter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.primitives.DynamicEnumParameter<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicDataDisplayOperationIdEnumParameter, DynamicDataImportOperationIdEnumParameter, DynamicStringEnumParameter, ProjectsSettings.ProjectTemplateEnum, TableColumnConversionParameter, TableColumnIntegrationParameter, UIPlotDataSeriesColumnEnum

    public abstract class DynamicEnumParameter<T>
extends Object
    Parameter that acts as dynamic enum. Use DynamicEnumParameterSettings to define a supplier for the items. Alternatively, use allowedValues to supply items. allowedValues is preferred. If allowedValues is null, you have to use DynamicEnumParameterSettings.
